<div class="list-pages-item">


<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00400/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>项目描述：</strong>一颗无论用什么方式都无法让其进入篮筐的篮球。<br />
<strong>回收日期：</strong>20██/██/██<br />
<strong>回收地点：</strong>Site-CN-01与Site-CN-02友谊篮球赛赛场。<br />
<strong>当前状态：</strong>在比赛时一名队员尝试球不离开手强行塞入篮筐<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-285506-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-285506-1')">1</a></sup>时爆炸。<br />
<strong>笔记：</strong><em>这个球是Site-CN-01与Site-CN-02友谊篮球赛时Site-CN-01在领先时Site-CN-01要求换的球。要不是这个知道这个消息，我都怀疑人生了。</em>——Site-CN-02尝试扣篮的球员</p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span id="u-credit-00400" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00400" target="_blank">编辑</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00400-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tian-xiu233" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6240575); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6240575&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610162813" alt="tian xiu233" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6240575)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tian-xiu233" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6240575); return false;">tian xiu233</a></span></p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong><span class="odate time_1600595491 format_%25Y-%25m-%25d">20 Sep 2020 09:51</span></p>
